txt.en: You have become a proficient Journeyman Tailor! You may now use Expert Tailor recipes, or continue to work towards Journeyman Tailor mastery.\n\nAdditionally, you are now eligible to join the <rgb=#00FF00>Tailor's Guild</rgb>, a special reputation faction open only to Expert Tailors. To join the Tailor's Guild, seek out a Master or Mistress of Crafting Guilds.
